    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for an initial 20-25 min or until softened and starting to colour</p><p>Tip: Stir the aubergine halfway through for even cooking!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1653319102516-x200.jpg",
