            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>diced shallot</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Add your<strong> red</strong> <strong>Thai curry paste </strong>and <strong>curry powder </strong>and cook for 1 min further or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1653319122852-x200.jpg",
