            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[600ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml] </span>of <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Rinse your <strong>red lentils</strong> in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 10-12 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1653319131973-x200.jpg",
