            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 20-25 min, remove the <strong>roasted aubergine </strong>from the oven and add the <strong>lentil mixture </strong>to the dish</p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then carefully layer the <strong>softened sliced potatoes</strong> on top (they will be hot!)</p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 10 min further or until everything's bubbling and the potatoes are brown and crispy – this is your <strong>Thai-style curry aubergine pie</strong></p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
